# Crispy Gochujang Tofu Bowls

Based on [School Night Vegan - Easy Tofu Marinades](https://schoolnightvegan.com/home/easy-tofu-marinades) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260112215657/https://schoolnightvegan.com/home/easy-tofu-marinades/))

